= !TextileMacro =

== Description ==

The !TextileMacro package implements the ability to use [http://thresholdstate.com/articles/4312/the-textile-reference-manual Textile]
within Trac.

== Installation ==

== Configuration ==

Enable the macro in:

/trac/env/Project/conf/trac.ini:

{{{
[components]
Textile.* = enabled
}}}

You may have to restart your Web server.

== Examples ==

{{{
{{{
#!Textile

|_. a|_. table|_. heading|
|a|table|row|

Here's "a link":tstate, and
"another link":tstate to the same site.

[tstate]http://thresholdstate.com/

}}}
}}}

== See Also ==
 * [http://thresholdstate.com/articles/4312/the-textile-reference-manual Textile reference manual]
 * [http://loopcore.com/python-textile/ Python Textile]

